Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================AVANT====================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,阿里巴巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,认识吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,阿拉丁 好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,能先把乌戈收起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我的伙伴都吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 别听他的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 阿里巴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.01,0:00:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我来找你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有好多话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得那个时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,约好了要一起去看世界是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 阿拉丁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法遵守约定了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,国军来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 阿里巴巴 闪人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.56,0:01:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,严格与礼节的精灵啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.36,0:01:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,命汝与汝之眷属
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,以吾魔力为粮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,赋予吾意志强大的力量吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,出来吧 亚蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,火 火炎的巨人啊！
